column10: Pervasive Health Conference is a premier international forum with specific focus on technologies and human factors related to the use of ubiquitous computing in healthcare and for wellbeing. The overall goal of the Pervasive Health Conference is to take a multidisciplinary approach to Pervasive Healthcare Technology research and development.

column10: The Eiffel Tower is an iron lattice tower located on the Champ de Mars in Paris. It was initially criticised by some of France leading artists and intellectuals for its design; but has become both a global cultural icon of France and one of the most recognizable structure in the world.
